{"tid":2203022,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"被控不小心駕駛新巴司機將於九龍城裁判法院提堂","createTime":"2020-09-15T05:05:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-15T05:34:35.000Z","uid":51271,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"02533f53c3f7a53bdb802cd2ad264d36964ceff3","tid":2203022,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T05:05:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1549668-20200915.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1549668-20200915.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=ulKCtXgG4rwmRR8qyGKIuZUrr29XULmfQ5XcAAvzh4c%3D&h=f5d9555e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1549668-20200915.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=fa8b3be7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1549668-20200915.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n一名新巴司機早前在九龍遊行期間，涉嫌危險駕駛被捕，亦被指涉嫌藏有攻擊性武器，其後被起訴不小心駕駛，今日將在九龍城裁判法院提堂。<br />\n<br />\n36歲被告張浩然，報稱是專營巴士司機，他被控於今年9月6日在油麻地彌敦道南行、近文明里在道路上不小心駕駛一輛新巴。<br />\n<br />\n有網民發起在9月6日下午在九龍區遊行，警方當日在彌敦道，登上一輛970號巴士截查，司機其後被警方帶走。"},{"pid":"7ba76c2da58cbfed2141c1ecd6ec19c662700df4","tid":2203022,"uid":34147,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T05:07:34.000Z","msg":"老不好小事<br />\n揸得車要入你嘅話根本走唔甩<br />\n大包圍 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a943a880f9c1fe3e470af51af2702e22a4d2983","tid":2203022,"uid":161726,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7ba76c2da58cbfed2141c1ecd6ec19c662700df4","tid":2203022,"uid":34147,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T05:07:34.000Z","msg":"老不好小事<br />\n揸得車要入你嘅話根本走唔甩<br />\n大包圍 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T05:10:08.000Z","msg":"罰則係點<br />\n罰錢定要坐?<br />\n如果扣分冇得返工都仆街"},{"pid":"9aa80c35cdd6f79e8b9e202a874e2542bc790aa4","tid":2203022,"uid":75,"like":